data.description: Location, location in highly desirable Tamarack Lakes neighborhood...great curb appeal will greet you as you pull up to this beautiful 3 sides brick and stone   4BR/3.5BA home nestled on almost 3/4 acre premium lot,,,as you enter you will find a 2 story entrance with formal living room to your left and formal dining   room to your right that flows into 2 story family room featuring cofered ceiling and cozy gas log fire place...main level boasts crown molding and hardwood  floors throughout except carpet in bedrooms and ceramic tile in baths...spacious owner's suite with sitting area and full bath with jetted tub/sep. shower, dual  vanities plus 2 additional bedrooms and kitchen with sleek granite counters, gas stove, stained cabinets and pantry plus laundry room complete main level...  upstairs is a large guest bedroom with full bath and walk in closet...unfinished basement for future expansion...you will love the huge backyard for outdoor fun,,,  ..wonderful screen porch to enjoy your morning coffee...must see to appreciate, you will love the lifestyle at Tamarack Lakes...Welcome home!!!THIS HOME IS PRICED BELOW RECENT APPRAISAL!!! MOTIVATED SELLER IS OFFERING $5,000. TOWARDS BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS!! THIS LOVELY  HOME HAS A BRAND NEW WATER AND 2 NEW AC UNITS, NEW ROOF IN 2022!! MAKE OFFER!!!
